    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dings. The interior shows clear signs of use, including worn upholstery. Mechanically, the car is operational, though it may require maintenance in the near future.",
